title: Who Are the 'MAGA Republicans' Biden Is Targeting?
description: Are you a "MAGA" Republican? Or really any kind of Republican? If you are, Joe Biden hates you and thinks you are a domestic enemy. Get ready, because Crowder is coming in hot. Also, there was a mass stabbing in Canada, where the prime minister says citizens don't have a right to self-defense. And a lesbian gets her tubes tied.
